Description_lang: Takazj flings sticky knots of webbing throughout the chamber, slowing players’ movement speed by $454311s1% and and inflicting $454311s2 Physical damage every $454311t2 sec while within the area.The central knot erupts when touched, inflicting $s1 Nature damage to players within $A1 yards and binding two players together in $@spellname440001.If Anub'arash charges through strands of Binding Webs, he becomes Entangled.
